# Toggle тАФ Visual Spec

## CSS classes

- `.acko-toggle` тАФ base, inline-flex, rounded-full, transition
- `.acko-toggle-sm` тАФ scale-32, font-label-md
- `.acko-toggle-md` тАФ scale-40, font-body-sm
- `.acko-toggle-lg` тАФ scale-48, font-body-md
- `.acko-toggle-default` тАФ toggle-bg, toggle-text
- `.acko-toggle-default.acko-toggle-pressed` тАФ toggle-active-bg, toggle-active-text
- `.acko-toggle-outline` тАФ transparent, border
- `.acko-toggle-outline.acko-toggle-pressed` тАФ toggle-active-bg
- Hover: toggle-bg-hover
- Focus: box-shadow primary-ring
- `.acko-toggle-disabled` тАФ opacity, cursor
- `.acko-toggle-group` тАФ inline-flex, gap space-1
